  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SpyEventHandler

    public class ReactArezConsoleSpyEventProcessor
extends ConsoleSpyEventProcessor
    A customized console event processor that avoids accessing "key" and "ref" attributes. This causes warnings when accessing props.key and props.ref in react components.
